Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:05.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear viewers, feast your eyes upon this ultimate super-lightweight machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:08.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This state-of-the-art aerofoil able to convert even a crosswind to a forward thrust...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:10.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This saddle of pure molded carbon-fiber with no synthetic leather...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:13.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This pursuit of function and form that has merged into a single work of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:16.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It goes without saying that to obtain \Nsuch a machine required much sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:17.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ignoring my studies, laboring at part-time jobs,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:20.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,sparing not a second for anything other than my time on the bike...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:21.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I risked it all to obtain this machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:23.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this weekend is the Shimanami Cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:24.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My win there is almost guaranteed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And at the end of my winning run I'll finally \Nbe greeted by that rose-colored campus life!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:31.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, can you bring it up? It's open...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:34.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am prepared for any contingency.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:36.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This lock is unbreakable, \Nsave for using a hydraulic cutter...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:40.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:42.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's my bicycle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:44.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't steal away my two years!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.31,0:00:49.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.78,0:00:55.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And just like that, the crystallization of my past two years goes down the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:57.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are called the Cheery Cycle Cleanup Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:59.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mysterious autonomous circle that regulates illegal bicycle parking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:01.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first they were a group staffed by volunteers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:03.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,diligently giving their time to maintain the campus,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:05.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but in recent years they've taken on a strange look,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:08.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and forcibly remove any bicycle just a tad outside the designated area...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:10.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And those bicycles are never to be seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:12.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rumors are that they end up at bicycle rental shops around Kyoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,or are transported across the Sea of Japan and sold to that country in the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:17.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lately they've expanded their influence beyond the campus to the entire city of Kyoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:19.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,so one cannot let down one's guard even when venturing off-campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:24.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\move(1161.419624,171.635688,1142.379958,125.464684)\bord0\be2\fs68.252788\t(\fscx108\fscy108)\c&H51358E&\fnDance Craze BV}Watch out for this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:24.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\move(164.34238,7.026022,70.141962,-55.223048)\bord0\be2\fs30.111524\t(\fscx108\fscy108)\fnDance Craze BV\b0\c&H1E2120&\t(\fscx108\fscy108)}Never forgive! \NCycle Cleanup Corps
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:21.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are the hated enemy of all Kyoto college students,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:24.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a threat to our peaceful daily lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:26.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why has such a thing happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:28.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is necessary for me to \Nquestion the one responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:29.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is responsible for this?
