Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I was a brand-spanking new freshman university student
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:07.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and before my eyes were innumerable open doors to that rose-colored campus life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:08.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, ever since I learned I'd passed the entrance exam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:11.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,my heart had already been set on the allure of a single circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that circle's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:18.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an6\pos(886.847599,208.773234)\fad(0,1400)\fs110.408922\bord0\be2\fnArista 2.0\c&HB73E82&\t(1000,2000,\c&HBF529C&)}Cycling Club \N{\fnBlackChancery\c&HB84587&\t(1000,2000,\c&HBF529C&)}Soleil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:19.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There lay my future of pure, sparking gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:21.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Together with the raven-haired maidens in love rendezvous' fierce contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:24.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the situation called for it, I'd even be \Nwilling to let them ride sitting behind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:28.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,...is what I, an idiot beyond all redemption, had thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:32.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Icarus's wings made of hardened wax melted after he single-mindedly flew straight toward the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:34.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I in pursuit of that rose-colored \Ncampus life was indeed no different,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:38.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,for the Cycling Club was a club in name only; it was more like a hard-core cycling team.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:44.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was cast quickly into despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:47.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and before my feet was a creature with a \Nface like a fish-man just risen from the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fiend! Sink back into the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You say some pretty mean things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am your compatriot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:59.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was my first contact with Ozu, \Nas well as worst contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:04.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they find fun about rotating their legs so fast they wear away the cartilage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's do something more fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:08.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go on a run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:14.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you resist it, there's no escaping your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Training was as harsh as you could imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was with the belief that \NI could overcome the suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:21.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and reach my rose-colored future that I turned the pedals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:24.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the world of "roadies," \Nonly the fast are recognized and praised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:27.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speed is king! Speed is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:31.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In high school I didn't belong to any sports clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:32.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact, I did as few activities as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:37.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and just stayed cooped up with a bunch of other layabout guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:41.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So a full-blown athletic team was far too heavy a burden for me to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even attempting to train,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,with my feeble constitution there was no certainty of improvement to begin with,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:47.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and of course there was no way I'd place well in any competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:51.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so I shuffled along, wasting my freshman year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:59.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,As usual all you're eating is chicken like a damn fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up, this is the best source of protein!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:05.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, my... Must be a struggle for a poor fellow like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead of chicken, how about letting me eat some salted tongue with green onions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How 'bout you eat some of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:12.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu never showed his face in the circle, but he'd frequently show up in my room.
