Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\be2\c&H5854CA&\fscx290\fscy340\t(0,60,\fscx240\fscy240)\fnJME\frz347.722\move(1513.152401,-60.223048,1483.08977,0,59,60)}Eat \Nit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why? Because someone called Ozu's "Master" lives on the second floor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,of this boarding house, \Nand it seems Ozu comes to visit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:19.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I surmised he was probably a master at telling lewd jokes or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your eyebrows are raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why so tense?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:29.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I have no interest \Nin wasting my time like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:34.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How cruel. I put a lot of effort into \Nenjoying wasting my college years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you have no right to criticize me on that front.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:37.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't hold me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,God damn him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:45.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(499.039666,42.156134)\fad(200,0)\bord2.007435\be3\c&H000000&\3c&HD9F3FA&\be3\fnBangle}Bicycle Club
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:51.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In there was a cornucopia of information about all possible kinds of aerodynamic bicycle parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, how about I do battle with the specs of my bicycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it not a path of escape, \Neven for a weak person such as myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:04.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having seen the light, in my second year \NI embarked on a complete change of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:09.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thinking back on it now, it was only the beginning of yet greater unhappiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:13.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,To get your hands on a good bicycle takes money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:16.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A reduction of a mere 1 or 2 grams \Nrequires an immense amount of funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:17.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Replacing the wheels, tires, \Nand shoes with lighter versions...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:19.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The handlebar, the stem, a compact crank...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,For me to obtain a somewhat decent bicycle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:24.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I left my studies to the side and dove into every part-time job there was,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:26.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,even dabbling in some illegal work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:29.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I became nothing more than a saving fiend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally in the winter of my second year, \Ntaking loans from my friends and acquaintances,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:34.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got my hands on the full-spec \Nmachine I had been dreaming of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What lightness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This bike is, indeed, my wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:41.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt that I could fly anywhere with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I had already heard the rumors of the Cheerful Cleanup Corps,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:48.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I took extreme caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:54.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so enamored with my new bicycle \NI'd take her out with me wherever I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this, Manami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had only let my guard down for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:10.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hadn't expected the Cleanup Corps \Nto go to such lengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:13.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would never see my beloved wheels again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this who I am now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:18.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the two years I have left, will I stay such a weakling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could not shut my eyes from that reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But nor could I stand to look on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:35.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you gone nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. On the contrary,\N I have seen the error of my ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had lost sight of something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bought two years ago at the university co-op,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,my Manami had been with me \Nthrough all my joys and sorrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:51.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I, once mad with visions of road bikes, would no longer be led astray.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manami is for me, my true life-partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:57.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(962.004175,44.163569)\bord3.011152\c&H454C71&\fsp5.018587\fnExpletive Deleted\fs100.371747\b0\3c&HF5F4F4&}Shimanami Cup
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:57.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But fate soon tore Manami and I apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manami... Have you seen my Manami?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't even consider it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it seems Manami was not \Nconsidered a participating bike
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:08.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and was transported to the finish area by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time I figured that out, a great deal of time had passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:14.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I started the race four hours late and it was already after lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:19.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Shimanami Cup goes from Onomichi to Shikoku, crossing the bridges from island to island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,After crossing one bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,you run along the coastline of the island, then climb up onto another bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:24.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's a strenuous up-down course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:27.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manami, why must you be so heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder where all the other racers are?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:36.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or wait, is the race even still going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? There's still people out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:45.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't need any entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though my only goal now was to stay on the course,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:50.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,as night fell I began to lose sight of the course indicators.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,For what reason was I racing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:54.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,For what reason did I even go to college?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manami? What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a cheap-ass basket-bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:08:59.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Continuing with the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:04.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today in Hiroshima prefecture, the 10th annual Shimanami Cup was held in Onomichi city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:06.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The 240 participants put on a fierce race,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:12.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and the winner with a splendid \Nvictory was Kyoto's Higuchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:16.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the crystallization of my past two years!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:19.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I worked hard for this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:23.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm very happy I could be victorious for my \Ndisciple who always cheered me on," he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough, enough! I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:32.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where had all this energy I'd expended the whole time vanished to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:33.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This violates the conservation of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does not compute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:37.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this not a blasphemy of modern physics?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:42.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,While I was thinking of such things, morning dawned, then night fell,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:46.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,then morning again, then night, \Nand when I came to, I had reached Kyamachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:52.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your face is a face of extreme impatience... You are unsatisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:56.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can sense your fiercely earnest talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quickly I did tip my hat to the old woman's keen insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:02.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyways, I sense there is an \Nopportunity you can't let pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:03.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:07.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This opportunity is always \Ndangling in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:09.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please grab it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That'll be 3,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:13.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You raised the prices again? And damn that was quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:16.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seemed that I had somehow fallen into the sea of worthlessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:20.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps I had never even taken off to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:27.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end I was fated to waste away my college life just as Ozu had said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:40.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for abducting you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:43.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm taking you to my circle's shack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:46.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have a serious favor to ask you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:50.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akashi-san was a student in the engineering department one year below me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The previous year she was the sole female member registered to Soleil,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:56.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and amazingly won the overall victory at a road race held in Keage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:59.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you going to use the prize money for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for me to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:04.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had sturdy legs and an air \Nthat didn't let others get near her,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she had no real interest in races and quit Soleil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:10.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She invested all the prize money in her current circle, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:12.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:19.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for the shady look of the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:34.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've brought him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:37.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You? You're the dropout from Soleil?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:38.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our club president.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:43.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, you really do have a feeble body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:46.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're exactly the kind of man perfect to become a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:47.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Become a bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:50.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome to our Birdman Team!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:55.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weight, 59 kilograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:56.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chest, 80 centimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waist, 70 centimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:00.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed, you have the ideal body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:02.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What in the world is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:06.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akashi-kun is our star engineer, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:08.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she seems to be interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:11.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have the airframe almost completed, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:15.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no one in the team is suitable to pilot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:17.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do anything in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:21.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So will you pilot it, with that perfect body you have right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to get in that plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:27.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm a complete weakling. \NI even dropped out from Soleil...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:28.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:31.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need our pilot to be as frail as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:36.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not all, but you are definitely our ideal pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:37.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is no special training you will need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:41.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Simply come to the competition as you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:45.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just take care of your body so you don't get the flu, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a sudden development.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It did feel a bit like I was forced into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:55.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and isn't this just a nice way of saying "you're a stone falling into a lake"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Birdman contest is a cruel game where you pedal and pedal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,until you inevitably drop into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, it didn't have to be me; \Nit could have been anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:04.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And isn't it really scary to head straight into the sea from such a height?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's unbearable! I can't take losing anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:15.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was spring of last year, \Nduring the road race on Keage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:17.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had taken off with a good speed at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:21.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I immediately got winded, \Nand was staring up at the canal incline.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:24.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The power plant over there is quite wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:28.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's full of dubious machines, and stirs up my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's especially lovely during sakura season.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akashi-san, shouldn't you be in a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the favorite to win the women's race?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:37.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:39.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:42.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sakura are very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:46.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so Akashi-san won not only the \Nwomen's race, but the overall victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:49.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then I saw dangling from Akashi-san, the Mochiguman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:52.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They come in sets of five, \Nso it seemed like she had lost one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:57.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards I came across it, \Nand had continuously forgotten to return it till today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:14:02.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This opportunity is always \Ndangling in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:04.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This body has already crashed once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Falling is something I have firsthand knowledge of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I need to do is grit my teeth and launch with a shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:10.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then Akashi-san will surely come to me after I've fallen, with a smile on her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:14.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then afterwards, I'll sit behind Akashi-san as she rides up the sakura-lined incline!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! Can I allow myself to \Nbe addled by such feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:19.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your dreams shouldn't be so flimsy, weak, and limp noodled!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:22.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay to lower my future to such a shameless fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:25.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,To no longer shoot for the sun, but to live lazily on the ground? How is that Icarus?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:27.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd just be some kid with ugly-ass wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:32.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wavering in the gap between reality and fantasy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,exhausted by the tumultuous \Ndevelopments of the past few days
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and my no-rest, no-sleep return from Shikoku,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:38.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I fell to sleep like a sack of potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:42.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you keep up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:46.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This man is named Jougasaki, \Nand is president of the Movie Circle "Misogi".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:49.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a man that lives for \Nworking out and women's boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:50.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I asked him to teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, I'd made my decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd fly farther than anyone, higher than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And on the dawn of my victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:59.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akashi-san will be sitting on the back of Manami as we ride up the sakura-lined incline!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:02.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen up. Victory is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:06.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will not allow you to run from a battle and live aloof like that Higuchi guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:08.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're a man, then grab victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:11.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grab victory, and grab women's tits!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:14.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jougasaki-senpai's teachings were actually pretty clear-cut,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:16.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and my motivation rose to higher and higher levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:19.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Birdman contest was even televised, and the place for the circle to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I won, then I would no doubt gain the attention
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,of raven-haired maidens from all around Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:27.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet I'd need to broaden my field of vision to other women than just Akashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:29.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that is a trial all winners must face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:33.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Being the hero sure is tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said you were fine the way you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:50.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But now you've got muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything's ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:58.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akashi-kun's plane is designed with \Nextremely sensitive aviation tolerances!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:03.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even a 10-gram difference in the pilot would mean redoing the entire blueprint!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruined! It's all ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:08.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough! Akashi-kun, you be the pilot after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:12.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You and your muscles can get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:16.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I already had my hands full thinking up countermeasures to the Cleanup Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:18.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out of here, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:21.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akashi-kun, you hurry back to work, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:28.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for getting you involved in this weird stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:32.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize too, for not living up to your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:36.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, actually the problem was that you far surpassed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:41.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Birdman is, after all, an absurd goal \Nthat goes against the reason of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:45.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I was thinking that the pilot should be a person
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,with a soul charred by idleness and wasted passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:50.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that after you finished the Shimanami Cup on a basket-bike,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:52.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,you came all the way back from Shikoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:55.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's an incredible waste of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:57.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, that wasn't exactly my intention...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:01.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I asked you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:06.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the idea that you'd go so far as to train didn't figure into my calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose I still have a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:15.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize, but I have to redo the design now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:44.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it I had come to the Keage Incline.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had prayed to come here with Akashi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:50.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but now I felt like the rose-colored campus life was slipping yet even farther away,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:52.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and my heart wept within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'd be better off flowing down and trying and make my name
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:57.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,as an Egg-Pumpkin youkai that lives in Lake Biwa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:03.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Cleanup Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:04.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man in the trench coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:13.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oops, you caught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:18.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:20.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep it a secret, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:23.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an important source of \Nfunds for the Secret Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Akashi-san's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:31.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're in recession, so bicycles alone aren't cutting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:33.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:37.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A certain person up north is looking for a plane much like this to play with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:40.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just going to crash into Lake Biwa anyway, \Nso this is a far better use, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:43.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what about my bike?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:45.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who stole it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:48.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't really concern myself with each one individually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:49.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:51.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's how I show my love, so grab it while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, it doesn't matter which path you take,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,you'll keep ending up right where you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:57.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:01.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would it be so bad to give yourself up and go with the flow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:05.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're connected by the black thread of fate, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:06.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got debts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:11.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go around Kyoto collecting bicycles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:17.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only if I can aim mainly at \Ncouples riding two to a bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:20.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure thing! You do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess the jig's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:28.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like Akashi-san is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell anyone about the Cleanup Corps, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Might be bad for your health....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:33.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:37.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:49.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the trench coat man from the Cycle Cleanup Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:51.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No! That's not it! \NAkashi-san, this is a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:56.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it! The Cheery Cycle Cleanup Corps are actually—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:57.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:19:59.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Explain it to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:03.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:05.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai, where are the brakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:15.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:17.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jump off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:23.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this rate I'll crash into the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:26.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to try pedaling and fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:30.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now's the time for my training to pay off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are the pedals?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:42.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akashi-san, where are the pedals?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:47.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're in the free-flying category!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:52.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It finally dawned on me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:55.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,that this was all a truly wasted effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:58.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps this all started from the moment I considered the cycling club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:03.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I had joined some other circle, I would have surely spent quite a different two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:07.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meeting Ozu was clearly the greatest catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:11.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could Icarus have ridden the wind had \Nhe not tried to so hard to flap his wings?
